    "description": "《钓鱼喂猫》是一款第三人称休闲游戏，玩家将的公园里钓鱼，并吸引在公园的流浪猫前来，向您讨鱼吃。<br>公园环境：真实的3d场景，巨大的湖泊，清澈的湖水，以及阳光和树木。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054720/extras/768c238a7b315048a4d48e3aa4838ca4.poster.avif?t=1766164461\" width=614 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054720/extras/768c238a7b315048a4d48e3aa4838ca4.webm?t=1766164461\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054720/extras/768c238a7b315048a4d48e3aa4838ca4.mp4?t=1766164461\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>随着您的不断投喂，越来越多的猫咪前来讨鱼，与猫的亲密度提高后，您就可以给猫起个名字。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054720/extras/b4423972553bbbf7ef85b8aa307dacb0.poster.avif?t=1766164461\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054720/extras/b4423972553bbbf7ef85b8aa307dacb0.webm?t=1766164461\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054720/extras/b4423972553bbbf7ef85b8aa307dacb0.mp4?t=1766164461\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>抚摸猫猫：<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054720/extras/7fb2b130c3c54ef0d98909684243b3e4.poster.avif?t=1766164461\" width=634 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054720/extras/7fb2b130c3c54ef0d98909684243b3e4.webm?t=1766164461\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054720/extras/7fb2b130c3c54ef0d98909684243b3e4.mp4?t=1766164461\" type=\